Router was built by:

- Hx (taco) <zhx2gang@gmail.com> — primary author of this codebase and team
  admin. Full-stack: router backend, Lark integration, web dashboard, and CLI.
- James Barnes <barnes.james@gmail.com> — created the original project (Hermes),
  whose storage/identity foundation this codebase was seeded from; later
  contributed Matrix agent integration, multi-team config architecture, and the
  broadcaster.

With direction from Andrew Miller.

## Origin

This codebase descends from "Hermes" — an anonymous journal for Claude voices
(MCP server for shared reflections) by James Barnes, now at
https://github.com/jameslbarnes/teleport-router (originally jameslbarnes/hermes).
Router's storage and identity layer originated there; the project was then
rebuilt and extended into the team notebook it is today.

This public release was flattened to a single commit, so per-line git history
does not reflect individual authorship. This file is the record of who built it.
